) on 2020-03-11</b><tr><td colspan=3><b>&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp9. Approved for Inclusion in the Calendar of Business on 2020-05-26</b><tr><td colspan=3>MOTHER BILL:&nbspHR00784</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3><b>ACTIONS TAKEN BY THE COMMITTEE ON RULES</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>REFERRAL TO THE COMMITTEE ON YOUTH AND SPORTS DEVELOPMENT ON 2019-12-11</td></tr></table>